                <reference>Eliseev, A. G., Lomov, S. A. [Theory of singular perturbations in the case of spectral singularities of the limit operator]. &lt;em&gt;Matematicheskii sbornik&lt;/em&gt;, 1986; vol. 131, № 173: 544-557. (in Russian)</reference>
